Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:36.76,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:91259,96765}{\i1}DM Productions' performances in Tōhoku\Nhave increased Nozomi's popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:41.72,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:96765,101728}{\i1}However, when Nozomi had learned\Nof their underhanded ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:44.60,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:101728,104606}{\i1}she felt that her life\Nas a singer was in danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:47.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:104606,107693}{\i1}and in a daring escape,\Nshe jumped off the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:50.32,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:107693,110320}{\i1}Not long after, she was found\Nnear the tracks by Kumagorō.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.37,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:124167,125377}Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:12.59,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:125377,132592}{\fad(0,2000)}— Episode 13 —\NThe Grass That Grows Again{NOTE:第13話\\Nふまれた野の草}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.67,0:02:17.09,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:134678,137097}Be more careful, Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:20.01,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:137097,140016}Don't let go of Mom's hand. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:23.81,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:140016,143812}I know!\NYou too, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:26.81,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:144563,146815}Welcome! Here's a little riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:31.36,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:146815,151361}Which fruit contain the most vitamin C:\Nlemons, apples or strawberries?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:33.23,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:151361,153238}– Apples. – Lemons.\N– Strawberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:34.78,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:153238,154781}Correct! It's strawberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:36.03,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:154781,156032}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:38.49,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:156032,158493}But I can't give you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.66,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:158493,160662}The reward of this quiz\Nis what you have just learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.88,Default,Flower shop owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:172007,175886}Mine-san… I wonder if having\Na side job is a good idea for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.42,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:175886,177429}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.97,Default,Flower shop owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:177429,179973}Here, see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.09,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:179973,181099}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.43,Default,Flower shop owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:183018,186438}We really can't afford\Nselling flowers like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:09.85,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:187647,189858}I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:12.36,Default,Flower shop owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:189858,192360}Our profit is very small.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:17.11,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:192360,197115}If we offer merchandise like that,\Nwe won't earn a single penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.49,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:197115,199493}Please, give me one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.49,0:03:23.58,Default,Flower shop owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:199493,203580}But if take your time to redo it,\Nyou won't be able to work at the oden stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:28.66,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:203580,208668}Mister, it's my fault.\NI'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:29.71,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:208668,209711}Yuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:34.00,Default,Flower shop owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:209711,214007}Oh, Yuki-chan, you're such\Na good child, helping your mom out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:40.13,Default,Flower shop owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:216676,220138}We'll need to deliver them very soon.\NIs it really okay for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.80,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:220138,221807}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:45.22,Default,Flower shop owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:221807,225227}I'm also worried about\Nyour eyes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.89,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:225227,226895}T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.94,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:231066,233944}Come on, come on!\NHurry up, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.78,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:237405,239783}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.20,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:247332,249209}Come on, cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:11.96,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:249209,251962}It's not like you, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:13.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:251962,253922}I'm sorry, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.63,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:255173,256633}Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:257676,260887}I just thought that shortly\NI'll finally be back in Tōkyō, and… yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:265267,267394}I need to start over. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:271773,274901}This time around,\Nit'll be much more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:41.90,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:278321,281908}Wow, look at that mandarin, so sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:44.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:281908,284369}I'm sorry, I've been only\Ndragging you into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.16,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:284369,286162}Oh, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:49.37,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:286162,289374}Maybe you didn't get the money,\Nbut your songs were the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:53.04,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:289374,293044}Don't worry about\Nyour uncle, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.01,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:307434,308018}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.64,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:312606,313648}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:22.24,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:318111,322240}"Tonan Hospital,\NAccounting Division".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:32.75,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:328580,332751}"Long-term hospitalization expenses"…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.71,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:335170,337714}"The bill for this month"…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:40.92,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:337714,340926}"No payment"…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.56,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:354147,355565}Mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:58.44,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:355565,358443}– Mommy! Mommy!\N– I'm fine. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.40,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:361613,363406}What's going on, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.11,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:363406,364115}Never mind—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.99,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:364115,365992}You can't overwork, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:08.82,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:365992,368828}Yuki, get the futon. Quick, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.16,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:368828,370163}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.54,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:374918,376544}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:22.21,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:378838,382217}It's okay, it's okay.\NI'll take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.81,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:393019,394813}Lights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:43.11,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:399818,403113}Good, but let's move your arms a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:45.69,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:403947,405699}Alright, Miki-san, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:46.49,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:405699,406491}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:55.58,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:413999,415583}Alright, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:57.04,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:415583,417043}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.16,Default,Photographer,0,0,0,,{TIME:417043,418169}Oh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.88,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:420422,423883}Let's drop by the advertisement\Ndepartment on our way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.17,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:423883,425176}Good call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:10.68,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:427804,430682}We've just finished a photo shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.30,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:431307,433309}I see. That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:18.85,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:433309,438857}Nohara-san, we'd love for you to compose\Nalso other songs beyond the one for her debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.02,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:438857,441026}Of course, if I have the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:23.36,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:441026,443361}Are you still seeing Mr. Egawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:24.57,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:443361,444571}Yes, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.82,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:444571,446823}Do you get the feeling\Nthat he's changed lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.24,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:446823,448241}– Not really.\N– Changed how?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.24,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:448241,449242}Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.45,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:449242,451453}You're so funny, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:38.91,Default,Random old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:455457,458918}H-Hey, Mr. Nohara!\NPlease wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:43.29,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:460462,463298}{\an2\fad(0,2000)}Ueno Station{NOTE:上野駅}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.51,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:467469,470513}What's wrong?\NWe're finally back home, in Tōkyō.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:54.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:470513,474100}In the end I didn't bring\Na single souvenir with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.51,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:474100,476519}Don't worry about it.\NWhat else you could have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:57.72,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:476519,477729}Hey, taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:477729,479564}Kuma-san! A taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.02,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:479564,481024}It's okay, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:04.06,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:481024,484069}When to take luxury\Nif not in moments like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.48,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:484069,485487}Hey, hey! Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:15.66,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:491409,495663}If you don't cheer up a little, Nozomi-chan,\Nyou're gonna disappoint your folks at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:495663,496164}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:20.46,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:496164,500460}And when I see that Nohara fella again,\NI'm gonna crush his guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:500460,501753}Kuma-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.67,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:501753,502670}I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:25.17,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:502670,505173}I can't believe what he's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:29.88,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:505173,509886}How he introduced you to such\Na dirty production company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.84,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:509886,511846}I'm gonna remodel\Nthat pretty face of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:511846,514641}But it was me who asked him for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:38.72,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:514641,518728}No. Even if asked, he shouldn't have\Nintroduced you to those bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:42.89,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:518728,522899}Don't you think? Besides he trampled\Non your teacher's honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.15,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:522899,524150}Right, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:45.23,Default,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:524150,525235}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:46.31,Default,Taxi driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:525235,526319}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:526319,527278}{\i1}Mr. Egawa…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:52.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:529280,532033}I can't go back to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.61,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:532575,534619}Egawa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.53,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:534619,536538}Mr. Egawa, hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:13.97,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:552971,553972}What is it, Sune?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:18.14,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:554848,558143}Uhm, I'm here with your coffee, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.47,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:558143,559477}Do you have any news?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:23.10,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:560353,563106}There were two calls\Nabout your schedule today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:26.27,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:563106,566276}one from a record company\Nand the other from a TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.73,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:566276,567735}What about Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.19,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:567735,569195}Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:31.23,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:570029,571239}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.19,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:571239,572198}Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:40.66,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:577829,580665}If she dares to appear here again,\Ndon't let her in, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.16,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:582208,583168}Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.66,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:583668,584669}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.75,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:587964,589757}Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:01.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:598266,601686}Kuma-san, thank you\Nfor everything you do for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.02,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:602020,603021}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:603021,604189}I'm truly thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.65,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:608359,610653}Stop it, we've known\Neach other forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.94,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:610653,612947}Now lighten up, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:14.69,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:613573,614699}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:17.45,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:614699,617452}Go see your folks now.\NThey must be worried sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:21.45,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:618369,621456}Don't worry about the future now.\NTake your time, you'll think about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:23.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:622707,623750}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:626294,627754}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.50,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:627754,628504}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:36.97,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:632008,636971}Don't write Mr. Egawa off just yet.\NMaybe he'll take you in again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:638973,640683}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:43.72,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:640683,643728}Tell Yuki-chan and Kazu-chan I said hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:643728,644896}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.01,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:655073,656015}Shit…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:20.81,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:675101,680815}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:25.06,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:680815,685069}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:26.21,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:685069,686212}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:30.40,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:689032,690408}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.28,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:693995,695288}Sis…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.08,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:695288,697081}Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:697081,698166}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:42.00,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:698666,702003}Welcome back.\NCome on, step inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.50,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:702003,703504}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:49.09,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:706007,709093}What's wrong, Sis?\NYou look sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:709469,710970}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:53.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:710970,713598}More importantly,\Nwhere's the oden stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:56.80,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:714641,716809}Oh, that? We sold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:57.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:716809,717685}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.14,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:717685,720146}We didn't have enough cash\Nto cover the medical bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:720146,721230}Did Mom really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:01.89,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:721230,721898}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:722941,724359}What about Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.44,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:724359,725443}She collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:725443,726861}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:07.73,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:726861,727737}She's lying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:13.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:732575,733868}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:18.91,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:737664,738915}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.50,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:746589,748508}Nozomi!
Comment: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:46.85,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:766859,766859}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:59.03,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:774450,779038}But you can't sit making flowers\Nall day long, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:779038,780540}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:04.96,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:780540,784961}You wanted to be a singer.\NYou have to look to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:08.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:784961,788214}But how can I have fun singing\Nwhen we have such problems at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:10.88,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:788214,790883}So you think that singing\Nis just fooling around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:791509,792885}I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.63,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:792885,795638}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:795638,797515}It's just that I feel so guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.89,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:797515,799892}That's only because\Nof that sketchy company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:23.89,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:801227,803896}Don't let money\Nbecome your first priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:803896,805606}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:29.15,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:805606,809152}I wasn't there for a just a moment\Nand you've grown so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.90,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:809152,811904}Alright. That was the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.90,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:813114,815908}You're done with this one too, right?\NI'll put it with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.91,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:823458,825918}Kazu-chan pretty much nailed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.62,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:825918,828629}You should focus\Non your career alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:828629,829922}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:56.92,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:831883,836929}No matter what happens, there's no harm\Nif you try to return to Mr. Egawa's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:03.01,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:839223,843019}That Nohara Jun fella is the bad guy here.\NIt's not you, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:04.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:843019,844729}Don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:844729,847106}He was only trying to be kind.\NI can't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.23,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:847106,849233}But still…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:12.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:849233,852111}I'm aware that my only option\Nis to sing all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:16.11,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:852695,856115}What else is there to think about, then?\NCome on, go and see Mr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:22.37,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:859118,862371}Listen. It's because everyone is trying\Nto fight against poverty,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:26.16,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:862371,866167}they're really looking forward\Nso much to see you succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:27.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:866918,867960}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:32.54,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:867960,872548}Then hurry up and go to\NMr. Egawa's place… ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:35.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:872548,875635}Kuma-san, you're right.\NI'll go and see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:38.34,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:875635,878346}Yeah! I think that's the best idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:50.56,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:889524,890566}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:53.82,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:890566,893820}Nozomi-chan?\NW-Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:58.03,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:895738,898032}What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.32,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:898032,900326}Come on, step inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:900326,902370}Thank you.\NYou've always been so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:16.50,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:913589,916509}So it was Nohara-san who\Nhas invited you, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:21.76,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:918136,921764}But I wonder if he can forgive you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:24.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:921764,924684}I left of my own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:924684,926686}I have no excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:30.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:928229,930022}One more chance is all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:31.39,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:930022,931399}Nozomi-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:931399,932483}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:37.98,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:933234,937989}While you were away, you could see\Nthat my master was very angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:42.74,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:937989,942743}but I think he was waiting for your return\Nand that's why he's been sulking all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:942743,944412}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.99,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:944412,946998}Remember: nothing ventured,\Nnothing gained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:48.95,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:947957,948958}Sune!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:49.95,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:948958,949959}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.00,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:949959,951002}Make me some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:52.50,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:951002,952503}Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.00,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:952503,954005}It's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.56,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:970897,972565}Any news from Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.86,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:981532,983868}Who gave you the permission\Nto enter this room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:26.66,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:983868,986662}Who has let you inside this house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:27.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:986662,987663}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:28.95,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:987663,988956}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:990583,992210}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:34.25,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:992210,994253}– I'm terribly—\N– Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.25,0:16:36.96,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:994253,996964}You're like some nocturnal animal,\Ndoing whatever you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:996964,998424}You…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:39.96,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:998424,999967}You ungrateful minx!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.13,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002511,1004138}Why are you still here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.89,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004138,1005890}I told you to get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:49.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006432,1009143}I have no words to defend myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:51.43,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009143,1011437}I just want to receive your scolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:01.57,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018945,1021572}Please forgive Nozomi-chan, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:04.95,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021572,1024951}There are things you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:07.41,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024951,1027411}What could it possibly be\Nto validate her actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:15.00,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031374,1035002}My work doesn't include giving in\Nto the whims of my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:18.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035795,1038798}I'm sorry I have disturbed you\Nduring your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038798,1040925}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:29.93,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046222,1049934}Master, do you know who was the person\Nwho had introduced Nozomi-chan to DM Pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.51,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050559,1051519}How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.72,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051519,1053729}It was Mr. Nohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.73,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053729,1054730}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.28,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062154,1063281}Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063281,1064240}Kuma-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:47.57,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064240,1067576}Ah, I see… It didn't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.58,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071622,1073582}What a melodrama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:57.71,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074000,1077712}What do you want?\NBugger off and leave us in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:59.21,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077712,1079213}I'm afraid I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.67,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079213,1082675}I can't be watching my classmate's\Ntragedy silently, now, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.80,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082675,1084802}Let's go, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:07.55,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086262,1087555}Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:10.64,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087555,1090641}Soon it'll be time for\Nmy debut at Uchida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:15.60,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090641,1095604}I know that Mine-san is in big trouble.\NI'm going to need an assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:17.23,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095604,1097231}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097231,1098774}An assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:19.60,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098774,1099608}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:24.36,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099608,1104363}When you become a star, you'll need to have\Nsomeone who will do the things around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:28.24,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104363,1108242}Don't talk nonsense.\NNozomi-chan, your secretary?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:31.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108242,1111037}I see… That's truly too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:31.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111037,1111954}We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.87,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113372,1115875}Let me know\Nif you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.71,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115875,1117710}I'm sure you'd make\Na great assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.80,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124675,1127803}You want to help Mine\Nas a fellow student?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:51.64,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127803,1131640}Yes. I was thinking of\Nhiring her as my assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.10,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131640,1133100}An assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.22,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133100,1134226}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:59.39,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134226,1139398}Don't. If you do that,\Nboth you and her will be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.31,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139398,1141317}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:04.94,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141317,1144945}I'm saying that you can't solve\Nevery problem with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.32,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144945,1147323}Your money will not\Nmake her any service.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:10.24,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147323,1150242}Why are you always…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.16,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150242,1151160}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:17.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155623,1157083}Asai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.21,Default,Asai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157083,1159210}Hey. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:20.71,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159210,1160711}Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161170,1162838}What's going on, Kazuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.34,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163672,1165341}Mom wanted to sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165341,1166801}Sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:30.59,Default,Asai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166801,1170596}Yes, she wanted us to come\Nand pick it up, so here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:33.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170596,1173224}I see. Please wait for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:34.97,Default,Asai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173724,1174975}Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:38.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177728,1178729}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:46.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184318,1186779}Mom! Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.95,Default,Mine Yuki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189907,1192952}Because we can't pay\Nfor Dad's doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:54.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193828,1194453}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.08,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196580,1198082}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:20:03.58,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198082,1203587}So if I disposed of what we no longer need,\Nwe could raise about 100,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203587,1204797}100,00 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:05.46,Default,Mine Shizuko,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204797,1205464}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:10.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207007,1210344}Mom, I'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.34,0:20:13.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210344,1213472}Little by little, I'll earn that sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.51,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213472,1216517}But they said we have\Nto pay it all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:20.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216517,1220521}I'll talk to them again.\NWe'll come up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220521,1221647}Right, Kazuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223607,1225401}Asai-kun, mister…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:27.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225401,1227027}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:29.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227027,1229029}Could you leave these here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:32.49,Default,Flower shop owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229029,1232491}No problem, but are you sure?\NWhat about the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:33.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232491,1233826}We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:36.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233826,1236537}I have my dear fans, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:37.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236537,1237663}Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:42.79,Default,Asai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241417,1242793}– Dad?\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:45.29,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1242793,1245296}– Yay!\N– It's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:48.09,Default,Asai,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245296,1248090}Shouldn't you be at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:50.25,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248632,1250259}Here's a riddle for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:54.22,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250259,1254221}Which has the most vitamin C:\Nlemons, strawberries or apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:56.34,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254221,1256348}Which one? Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:58.47,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256348,1258476}That's no good, Kuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:00.56,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258476,1260561}You can't copy me so shamelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:04.02,Default,Customer,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260561,1264023}He's right.\NIt's the boy's specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:05.52,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1264023,1265524}Alright, I don't wanna be any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:06.90,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265524,1266901}I won't lose to Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:10.19,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266901,1270196}Looks like she's decided to work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:13.19,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270196,1273199}Work? Nozomi-chan's working?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:14.28,Default,Kumagorō,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273199,1274283}Wait… Don't tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.70,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274658,1276702}Excuse me. Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:20.87,Default,Mine Kazuo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277244,1280873}Here's your favorite greengrocer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:25.04,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282458,1285044}It's me, Nohara.\NYou called for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.04,0:21:27.08,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285044,1287087}Yes. Step inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:33.01,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291592,1293010}What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:37.22,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295930,1297223}What on earth was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:40.89,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297223,1300893}I know you're the one who has introduced\NMine to DM Pro. I won't let that slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:47.85,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301936,1307858}But it was her who asked me to. She absolutely\Nneeded money to pay her father's hospital bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:50.19,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307858,1310194}With your experience,\Nyou should be ashamed of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:53.19,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310194,1313197}If someone asks you to work, do you show them\Nto the first swindler you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:58.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316116,1318702}Mine's returned\Nand she's a mess now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:01.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1318702,1321705}I have chased her out, on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:06.21,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323999,1326210}I chased Mine out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.25,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330256,1332258}I-I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:14.26,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332258,1334260}How is your apology going to help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.22,0:22:29.10,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345229,1349108}{\i1}Nozomi-san.\NI know you're in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:33.61,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351193,1353612}{\i1}But I'll be debuting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:37.61,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353612,1357616}{\i1}I'll need an assistant.\NHow about I hire you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.61,0:22:40.53,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357616,1360536}{\i1}I'm sure that\Nyou'll be a great assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:44.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361954,1364873}Before I become a singer,\NI need to find means to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:49.83,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364873,1369837}{\i1}It's difficult to imagine how Miki's proposal\Nmust have had hurt Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.83,0:22:53.84,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369837,1373841}{\i1}However, as a seventeen-year-old who was\Nthe only one able to take care of her family,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:57.09,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1373841,1377094}{\i1}even though she didn't want to\Nthrow her love for music out,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:00.51,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1377094,1380514}{\i1}it was the only sensible\Noption for Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:22:57.88,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1376135,1377886}Kōda
Comment: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:12.98,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1392985,1392985}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:20.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1394445,1400117}{\i1}Nozomi becomes an assistant to Kōda Miki,\Nwho steadily grows at Uchida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:24.83,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1400117,1404830}{\i1}Miki takes Nozomi to various meetings\Nwith TV stations and reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:29.75,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1404830,1409752}{\i1}But despite staying in the background,\NNozomi receives more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:33.92,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1409752,1413922}{\i1}Burning with jealousy, Miki points out\Nthat Nozomi's clothes are too conspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:38.63,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1413922,1418636}{\i1}She takes Nozomi to a store\Nto replace them immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:45.89,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1418636,1425893}{\i1}However, Nozomi doesn't know that\Nit was but a clever calculation on Miki's part.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:52.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1425893,1432691}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\NA Model Employee.{NOTE:涙のワンピース}
